        <li><a href="$!webPath/admin/advert_area_edit.htm" ><b>新增</b></a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
<!--   <div class="operation">
    <h3>友情提示</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>添加标识可通过article_标识.htm进行站内引用，标识不可重复</li>
    </ul>
